name: Stardust (itch) (PrinceTanis, Kate the Pan Plate)
description:
You're a spaceship flying through the stars, but your fuel tank has sprung a leak! The only way to get more fuel is through harvesting stardust extracted from the stars found around you!

Enemy spaceships also share the cosmos with you, and they're not friendly! Shoot them to learn where the enemy boss is, and take it down!
